# Vim notes

## Commands
```sh
# Basic commands
u  # Undo aka cmd+z

# Copy commands
yy   # Copy the current line in vi.
yiw  # Copy the current word
3yy  # Copy multiple lines in vim, type in the number of lines followed by yy.
y$   # Copy everything from the cursor to the end of the line.
y^   # Copy everything from the start of the line to the cursor.

# Word stuff
viw  # Visual select inner word
ciw  # Change inner word
diw  # Delete inner word
```
